Share an External App with an Enhanced Bot (Beta)

Use the custom messaging component to embed an app into bot conversations in enhanced Apple Messages for Business channels. Customers can access the app’s capabilities directly in the bot conversation.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Einstein Bots is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience. Setup for Einstein Bots is available in Lightning Experience.
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To build and manage Einstein Bots:
Customize Application
OR
Modify Metadata
OR
Manage Bots

NOTE This feature is a Beta Service. Customer may opt to try such Beta Service in its sole discretion.

From the Messaging Components page in Setup, create a custom messaging component.
From the Bot Builder, click Dialogs, and then select the dialog that you want to use to send the component.
From the Dialog Component Library, drag the Custom dialog step onto the canvas.
In the Step Properties panel, enter the name of your custom messaging component to search for and select it. If you don’t see your component, refresh the builder and try again.
Save your changes.
